        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "Require multipart package publishes",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Require `multipart/form-data` for `POST /api/v1/packages` and reject JSON package publish bodies before publish actions run.\n- Keep package artifact metadata server-created by rejecting public `artifact` payloads and deriving artifact hashes/integrity from uploaded bytes.\n- Preserve released CLI compatibility by accepting and sending the existing `files` and `clawpack` multipart fields, while also accepting `files[]` and `tarball` aliases.\n- Move browser plugin package publishing to multipart HTTP and update docs/spec coverage.\n\n## Tests\n\n- `bunx vitest run convex/httpApiV1.handlers.test.ts src/lib/packageUpload.test.ts src/__tests__/plugins-publish-route.test.tsx --reporter=dot`\n- `bun run --cwd packages/clawhub test:src -- src/cli/commands/packages.test.ts`\n- `bunx vitest run convex/httpApiV1.handlers.test.ts convex/lib/apiTokenAuth.test.ts src/__tests__/plugins-publish-route.test.tsx --reporter=dot`\n- `bunx tsc -p packages/clawhub/tsconfig.json --noEmit --pretty false`\n- `bun run format:check`\n- `bun run lint`\n- `git diff --check`\n- `git diff --cached --check`\n\n## Notes\n\n- `bunx tsc --noEmit` was attempted earlier. It is blocked locally by worktree dependency layout: Vite plugin types resolve from both this worktree and the sibling checkout `node_modules` path.\n",
